channel.title: SpaceEnviro V3
channel.description:
[b]Download the client here: http://www.datafilehost.com/download-fd5ed4ac.html[/b]
[center]Some Features[/center]
Working clues scrolls Most working skills Great community Great forums New summoning skill has been added. New hunter skill has been added - Quest will be required before skilling (Speak to Harrallak Menarous). Trees no longer chop off when you cut them. Run orb button removed. (Not needed as we have infinte run). Model heights fix for most NPCS/Players Items fixed (Some colours have been fixed.) Rune-Vortex style crest/blade. Bugged un-textured models fixed. Curses prayers 100% work. New shops in Edgeville (PK points and clothes store). Barrows now fixed. Disconnection bug fixed. Following returned to old way. King black dragon lair is now added. Emotes on most NPCs now full working. Potion mixing emote now added.
